                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-213" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WIGGETT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 126.) I took the prisoner, and saw her produce this shilling.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
